{"tid":1600733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我都忍口唔鬧公司班和理非做大台黃豬 佢地就成日衝衝子前 衝衝子後咁形容勇武派","createTime":"2019-09-28T17:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T18:43:13.000Z","uid":252492,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"756b7abf8ced86d7d6f76f65436004d1bfa54d4d","tid":1600733,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"見佢最近講到將公司物資捐比前線<br />\n我話捐比真係同警察對峙既ok<br />\n拿黎唱咩新國歌既無計傾<br />\n<br />\n佢就好似以為我係藍絲打壓佢咁 同我講佢都識衝衝子既前線<br />\n真係聽到我幾鬼銀耳 雖然我都由幾年前開始唔妥和理非<br />\n但e+興玩唔割蓆 唔可以鬧對家<br />\n<br />\n我地已經唔小班和理非成日唱k割蓆<br />\n佢地就成日屌鳩我地衝衝子 咩攪壞件事破壞個運動<br />\n<br />\n佢真係唔知和理非同勇武派幾年前開始幾大仇口<br />\n特別係旺角既憎金鐘既唱k豬憎到仆街<br />\n<br />\n但今時今日 兄弟爬山各自努力<br />\n兩邊人就唔該互相尊重<br />\n我覺得你地和理非大把資源又有612<br />\n<br />\n你話捐公司野比前線 我係真係想去到(前線) 到<br />\n唔係比班拿黎唱k無需要既人用<br />\n<br />\n正如捐錢我都叫人捐去星火<br />\n<br />\n佢就成日話唔妥我唔想見到我當我係藍絲<br />\n班和理非有時都癡鬼線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cf2db8d5fcacb5a88c8940e607033588f52478","tid":1600733,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24258af8913d7124a2b9700746380550833380d5","tid":1600733,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28983b28eb9b8f419e03cbe9a47596e1d1606aa3","tid":1600733,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:36:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人！！<br />\n<br />\n政府已經怕左美國人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係度扮會回應普選訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔好忘記共產黨係信唔過既盜國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有香港自治/香港獨立先可以得到5大訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />929 全球反共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />101 慶佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港自治，主權在民！<br />\n拯救香港，打倒共黨！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n香港獨立，還政於民！</span></span>"},{"pid":"4c4c3824492544d627e4c80bca3e7819f2010198","tid":1600733,"uid":27530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"同志，不是說好了後天才出分化貼子嗎？改了？單位沒通知我！"},{"pid":"dd18d868db2da8573531ac9f971056cd89096d69","tid":1600733,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c4c3824492544d627e4c80bca3e7819f2010198","tid":1600733,"uid":27530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:37:54.000Z","msg":"同志，不是說好了後天才出分化貼子嗎？改了？單位沒通知我！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:41:55.000Z","msg":"無呀 今日公司同事同我講佢話我係藍絲唔鍾意見到我先知<br />\n原來唔撐和理非佢地既行為就係藍絲<br />\n佢衝衝子前衝衝子後我都無屌佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1562f568dcb3bd370ca090e99688d3437737ff","tid":1600733,"uid":47110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"d14f30e1bb53a1ad90391497371fad95495e800d","tid":1600733,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a1562f568dcb3bd370ca090e99688d3437737ff","tid":1600733,"uid":47110,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\n拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T17:59:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},